# uv — this repo doesn't pin a lockfile; deps in pyproject.toml are loose
# and self-CI doesn't install the package (lint-test-python deleted in v3.1
# Task 2.5). Lockfile gets re-created locally on any `uv sync` and would
# churn without value.
uv.lock

